ussd-sender

A bash/zenity script as a GUI wrapper for huawei-ussd.pl, a perl script to send USSD code to 3G modems to check balance, recharge prepaid account etc...
The perl script and perl library dependency ( perl-gsm ) is included. You can run the GUI directly without installing this lib.

Please check if you're are member of the dialout group. If not:
```
sudo adduser YOUR_USER dialout
```
and log out and log in back to continue.
